msgctxt "QL_SandStorm_Desc"
msgid ""
"At the Kara Kara Bazaar, they say that the\n"
"sandstorm visible from camp hides a\n"
"<1.se_co>treasure left by the ancients<2.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"Keep close watch for when the sandstorm\n"
"disappears, and then quickly hunt for the\n"
"treasure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_SandStorm_Finish"
msgid ""
"The treasure sleeping in the sandstorm visible\n"
"from the Kara Kara Bazaar turned out to be an\n"
"ancient shrine.\n"
"\n"
"All that is left now is to overcome the\n"
"hero's trial within."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_SandStorm_Name"
msgid "The Eye of the Sandstorm"
msgstr ""

